Ma Bo.

29
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,150
You prick!

30
00:02:32,710 --> 00:02:34,470
How dare you hurt Song Chaoran?

31
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:44,340
=Lies Never Lie=
=Episode 4=

32
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:47,240
(Information)

33
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,030
Victim, Liu Cheng.

34
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:49,840
Psychological counselor
at Xinmei Institution.

35
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,400
He joined an intellectual disabilities

36
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,030
charity event held
by Women's Federation.

37
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:56,190
Wang Pu killed him on his way home

38
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:58,360
from a patient's house.

39
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,190
Keep reading.

40
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:03,190
Er...

41
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,960
Wang Pu, 48 years old.

42
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,800
Retired from the boxing team
18 years ago.

43
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,630
Due to his unsuccessful athletic career

44
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:10,180
and lack of skills to sustain himself,

45
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:11,590
he had a struggling life.

46
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,750
What about his family?

47
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,530
Unmarried.

48
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:16,280
His mother died of illness
when he was three,

49
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:18,560
and his father passed away
in a car accident when he was 22.

50
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,630
No siblings.

51
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,710
Master, the journey is quick.

52
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:32,590
I didn't know that.

53
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,630
Hurry up.

54
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,960
No time left.

55
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,520
Okay.

56
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:39,840
Wang Pu

57
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,710
joined the team in 1988.

58
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,190
1988?

59
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:47,520
When he was only 14?

60
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,080
Exactly.

61
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,430
He was specially recruited
by our old coach, Liu Haihua.

62
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:51,870
Wang Pu

63
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:54,750
was the hope of our municipal team
back then.

64
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:58,630
I can't believe he ended up a murderer.

65
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:02,120
Are you saying he was a genius?

66
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:05,190
Of course, he was specially recruited.

67
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,590
But based on what we found,

68
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:10,630
his athletic career was a failure.

69
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:12,960
(Champion)
It's a shame.

70
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,000
Coach Hu.

71
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,630
Yes?

72
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,600
This one?

73
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,190
Oh.

74
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,120
The leader found it unpleasant to display

75
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:23,870
a murderer's name,

76
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,480
so the trophy was turned around.

77
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,600
If what you say is true,

78
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:32,120
you two were in the same batch.

79
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:32,720
Yes.

80
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,310
You must be very skilled as well.

81
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:37,600
Why don't I see your name

82
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:40,190
on any certificates or medals?

83
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,600
Oh.

84
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:44,600
Well.

85
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:46,750
You see,

86
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,750
it's a funny coincidence.

87
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:50,720
Both of us

88
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:54,390
used to be known as Couch Liu's
most promising students.

89
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,950
But he preferred Wang Pu more.

90
00:04:56,950 --> 00:04:57,630
Fair enough.

91
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:59,720
He was very young

92
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:01,000
and gifted.

93
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,390
But I was the hard-working type.

94
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:05,360
That was why everyone
used to expect more from him.

95
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:06,750
May I ask you something?

96
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,600
Based on what you know about him,

97
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,830
did he ever show violent tendencies

98
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,270
outside the ring?

99
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,560
I'm not sure,

100
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,270
but he did hurt others by accident.

101
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,630
There was once,

102
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,560
during a selection competition,

103
00:05:26,330 --> 00:05:27,630
where one of us could be chosen.

104
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:30,870
It was a fierce fight between us.

105
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:32,000
Look.

106
00:05:32,190 --> 00:05:33,270
Twelve stitches.

107
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:36,830
It almost cost me my life.

108
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,920
I couldn't box anymore after that.

109
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,270
I had no choice but to be a coach.

110
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,870
I see. What about Wang Pu?

111
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,750
He didn't perform well

112
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,310
in that competition,

113
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:50,950
so he didn't win.

114
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:53,190
Afterward, people started
gossiping about him,

115
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:56,270
saying that he was bold
when beating his own teammates

116
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,560
but cowardly

117
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,720
when facing real opponents.

118
00:05:58,830 --> 00:05:59,680
Couch Liu even

119
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:02,120
called to talk to us several times
because of this.

120
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:06,000
It's fine for us to spar

121
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,560
and get hurt.

122
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,270
However, he hit someone in the street.

123
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,390
The victim was a layman.

124
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:11,750
That's too much.

125
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,270
Right?

126
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,190
You must know

127
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,390
Wang Pu was sentenced to death.

128
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,160
Master.

129
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,630
The execution is in two days.

130
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,830
Um,

131
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,160
after I was injured,

132
00:06:30,190 --> 00:06:31,430
I went back to my hometown.

133
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,120
By the time I returned,

134
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,000
he had already left.

135
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,120
I had never heard from him again.

136
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:43,430
(Boxing Gym)

137
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:45,070
Then Wang Pu wasn't wrongly accused.

138
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,830
Do you believe him?

139
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,680
I can analyze his facial expressions.

140
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,070
So he was lying,

141
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,360
and everything he said was fake?

142
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:58,800
Not entirely,

143
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,950
but he does hate Wang Pu.

144
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,310
That's why when he heard
about the execution,

145
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:04,510
he looked excited

146
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,800
and relieved.

147
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:08,160
It was like he finally got his revenge.

148
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,360
I can't analyze that much.

149
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,800
We didn't find anything useful
from Hu Tian.

150
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:17,310
I think I dislike Wang Pu more now.

151
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,510
Should the police

152
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:20,000
be less emotional?

153
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,390
You'll get used to it.

154
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:26,270
We didn't get much from Hu Tian,

155
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:29,120
just that he hates Wang Pu,
which doesn't help.

156
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:31,070
He mentioned Liu Haihua.

157
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:31,830
Right.

158
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,120
The coach.

159
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,720
Let's go.

160
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,680
Tiaotiao.

161
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,430
Yes?

162
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:40,040
Have you contacted
the local police station?

163
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:41,120
Yes, I did.

164
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,920
Good job.

165
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,360
Ms. Li, mind if I ask you something?

166
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,240
Shoot.

167
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:47,950
Aren't you worried

168
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,950
we might be wasting our time?

169
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:52,270
What makes you think that?

170
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:55,430
Liu Cheng was

171
00:07:55,430 --> 00:07:57,120
a quiet and decent man,

172
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,870
while Wang Pu looks fierce.

173
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:01,270
Even if something unexpected comes up,

174
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:04,240
I doubt the conviction
will be overturned.

175
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,750
As cops,

176
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:08,000
as long as there isn't
the slightest doubt left,

177
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,390
it's never a waste of time.

178
00:08:10,516 --> 00:08:14,440
(32 hours, 19 minutes
until Wang Pu's execution)

179
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:21,480
Ms. Wei.

180
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:21,800
Hmm.

181
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,560
Qian Pengfei, the man who assaulted Ma Bo,

182
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:26,000
is Song Chaoran's childhood friend
and business partner.

183
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:29,040
So he did this for his buddy?

184
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:32,030
What's interesting is that
according to Ma Bo,

185
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:34,000
Qian Pengfei made a private deal

186
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,550
to sell all his shares
to Tianniu Technology.

187
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,670
Why did you arrest me?

188
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,150
Ma Bo is the killer.

189
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,750
You assaulted someone.

190
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:54,080
Care to tell us why

191
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,910
you think Ma Bo is the killer?

192
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,000
Money.

193
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,270
What else can it be?

194
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:02,120
Ma Bo wanted to take over our company.

195
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,480
Chaoran refused,

196
00:09:03,550 --> 00:09:04,870
so he hired someone to beat him.

197
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:05,750
That's it.

198
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,240
An old trick in the book.

199
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,630
Song Chaoran refused to sell?

200
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:11,670
And what about you?

201
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:15,910
My shares are small. It doesn't matter
whether I sell them or not.

202
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:18,550
I'm asking, are you selling?

203
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:20,080
Yeah.

204
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:20,910
To whom?

205
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,360
Whoever pays the most.

206
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,480
From what we found,

207
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,670
Tianniu Technology offered
the highest price.

208
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,480
Fine, I admit

209
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,840
that Ma Bo and I

210
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,390
had a private deal,

211
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:35,960
and I'd sell my shares to him.

212
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,120
But Chaoran held the majority,

213
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:41,080
so I told Ma Bo I'd persuade Chaoran.

214
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,630
Looks like you failed.

215
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,550
Ma Bo took action against him

216
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:46,440
before I did anything.

217
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:50,080
How are you sure it was Ma Bo?

218
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:52,200
Who else could it be, then?

219
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,600
If you hadn't shown up so early,

220
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,260
I would've beaten him to a pulp.

221
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:55,790
Oh.

222
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:58,080
What about the shares now?

223
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:01,840
That's a different matter.

224
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:04,960
Chaoran and I are good buddies.

225
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:07,670
How could I not stand up for him
when he was bullied?

226
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,720
Arrest me or punish me

227
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:15,870
if you want.

228
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:17,320
I won't deny it.

229
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,030
Okay?

230
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:29,270
Captain Ding, we found the car
that moved Song Chaoran.

231
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:30,720
It belongs to Tianniu Technology.

232
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,200
The log shows

233
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,510
that the driver is Ma Da,

234
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:35,150
the brother of the deputy CEO, Ma Bo.

235
00:10:35,390 --> 00:10:36,200
Hmm.

236
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,240
Thank you, Coach Liu.

237
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,320
We came here

238
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,480
to ask about Wang Pu.

239
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,510
Wang Pu used to train under you...

240
00:10:58,510 --> 00:10:59,360
Dad,

241
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,720
why are you meeting with them?

242
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,480
It's about Wang Pu again?

243
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:07,200
You must be Liu Lin.

244
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:11,080
About your intention here,

245
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,910
I just want to say

246
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,360
that he deserves it.

247
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,750
Could you tell us why?

248
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,870
A murderer deserves to die.

249
00:11:20,150 --> 00:11:20,960
He had it coming.

250
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:25,840
That's all I have to say.

251
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:26,960
My dad knows nothing else.

252
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,360
Don't come back again.

253
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:29,960
My dad just recovered

254
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,150
from a stroke.

255
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:33,840
They're here to help Pu.

256
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:35,550
Dad,

257
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:38,150
he's not the Pu you knew anymore.

258
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,790
He's the murderer, Wang Pu.

259
00:11:42,150 --> 00:11:43,550
Wang Pu would never kill anyone.

260
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,440
I taught him before.

261
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:50,200
A boxer's fist should never
be used outside the ring.

262
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,360
As if he would listen to you.

263
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:52,790
Well.

264
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:55,960
If he had followed your teachings,

265
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,000
you wouldn't have left

266
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,840
Baizhou after spending
your whole life there.

267
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:00,320
He brought this trouble to you.

268
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:02,030
What trouble did he bring me?

269
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:02,870
Huh?

270
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:05,910
Since young,
whenever we bought some meat,

271
00:12:05,910 --> 00:12:07,870
he'd eat half of it.

272
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,080
And what?

273
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:10,840
He killed someone.

274
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,000
He was sentenced to death.

275
00:12:12,010 --> 00:12:12,840
That's easy for him.

276
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:13,670
What about you?

277
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:16,440
Your reputation is ruined.

278
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,910
I believe him.

279
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,720
He wouldn't do such a thing
when I say so.

280
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:23,000
Please calm down, Coach Liu.

281
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:28,120
We also believe Wang Pu
wouldn't kill without a reason.

282
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,150
Officers,

283
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,790
would you weigh in here?

284
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:35,080
I used to run a gym at Baizhou.

285
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:37,200
