447
00:20:33,830 --> 00:20:34,590
I don't know.

448
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,350
You don't know?

449
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:45,110
The car with plate number Bai A73548

450
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:49,920
