was you.

453
00:20:57,030 --> 00:21:00,030
Tell me, what were you doing
during those hours?

454
00:21:01,110 --> 00:21:02,070
Nothing.

455
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:03,680
I just drove around

456
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,590
