457
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:07,240
Where did you go?

458
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,440
I can't remember.

459
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,920
Let me refresh your memory.

460
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:12,680
Ziqiao Road,

461
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:14,830
Dongbing Road,

462
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:16,400
Shiwulidian,

463
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,310
Xiaguang Street,

464
00:21:18,310 --> 00:21:20,640
