- That's right.

513
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:49,880
Punch him.

514
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:52,270
Good.

515
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:53,270
(Brat,)

516
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:54,830
